<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>The druid has a mix of skills of pure caster, melee, and some of the ranger
skills. &nbsp; Each skill has a name, description, recommended point investment,
movement, needed for, and max formula.&nbsp; <b>Except for spell skills - you
will not be able to go over 200 until you reach level 51!</b></p>

<p>Enjoy!<br>
</p>

